Waxa ugu xiisaha badan, heerka calaamadaha (caafimaadka ilaa daran) ayaa si weyn uga hooseeyay kooxda WM+TCM marka loo eego kooxda WM oo keliya (7.4% vs 46.2%) iyo heerka dhimashada ayaa ka hooseeyay kooxda WM+TCM marka loo eego kooxda WM oo keliya (8.8% vs 39%).
