Bishii Diseembar 2019, waxaa ka dillaacay 2019 novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV), oo si rasmi ah loogu magac daray cudurka coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) iyo fayraska loo magacaabay Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
