Warbixin CNN ah ayaa tilmaamaysa in isku darka dadka waayeelka ah ee Talyaaniga iyo awooda aan la helin in la baaro tirada dadka qaba fayraska ilaa iyo hadda ay u badan tahay inay horseedayaan dhimashada sare.
