Ka dib markii gacmaha lagu qalajiyey waraaq gacmeed gacmaha lagu maydho, celcelis ahaan ilaa 76% guud ahaan bakteeriyada ayaa hoos u dhacday faraha iyo 77% gacmaha. Cilmi-baadhayaashu waxay sidoo kale sameeyeen tijaabooyin si ay u caddeeyaan haddii ay jirto suurtagalnimada wasakheynta (cross-contamination) ee ka soo baxa dadka kale ee isticmaala musqusha iyo deegaanka musqusha ee ka soo baxa goobta.
Qalabka qalajiyaha hawada ee jet-ka ah, oo hawada ka soo saara xawaare joogto ah oo ah 180 m / s (650 km / h; 400 mph), wuxuu awoodaa inuu ka tuuro jeermiska gacmaha iyo cutubyada, wuxuuna baabi'in karaa wasakheynta suurtagalka ah ee isticmaaleyaasha musqusha iyo deegaanka musqusha ilaa 2 mitir.
