BAngiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa kiciye ku xiran unugyada sanbabada, wadnaha, kelyaha iyo unugyada kale ee ku jira unugyada (cellular membranes).
ACE2 waxay diiddaa shaqada enzyme-ka angio-transforming enzyme (ACE) ee la xiriira iyadoo hoos u dhigeysa xaddiga angio-tencin-II waxayna kordhisaa Ang ((1-7) taas oo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed daawo oo rajo leh oo loogu talagalay daaweynta cudurada wadnaha. ACE2 waxay sidoo kale u shaqeysaa inay noqoto meel lagu galo unugyada qaar ka mid ah coronavirus.
Nooca bini'aadamka ee enzyme-ka waxaa badanaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 waa metalloloenzyme zinc-ku-xiran oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
Badeecada ACE2 waxay leedahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal kalectin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa borotiinka xarkaha ee nooca I ee hal-marka ah, oo goobta firfircoon ee waxqabadka kicinta ay ku jirto unugyada sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Dhinaca kale, ACE2 waxaa ka soo baxa dhinaca kale ee loo yaqaan 'shades' oo ka soo baxa dhinaca kale ee loo yaqaan 'transmembrane domain' waxaana ka soo baxa borotiinka lagu milmi karo ee lagu sii daayo dhiigga, ugu dambeynna lagu sii daayo dhexda ka soo baxa.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa xubnaha badankood: ACE2 waxay si weyn ugu xirantahay xuubka unugyada la xiriira alveoliga nooca II ee sanbabada, enterocytes-ka mindhicirka yar, unugyada arteries iyo endothelial ee xididdada badankood iyo unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee xididdada.
ACE2 mRNA waxaa lagu muujiyaa xitaa qalfoofka maskaxda, xayawaanka, hypothalamus iyo maskaxda.
Shaqada ugu weyn ee ACE2 waa inay noqoto mid isku dheelitiraya ACE.
ACE waxay u kala qaybisay hormoonka angiotensin I ee loo yaqaan 'Vasokonstricting angiotensin II'.
ACE2 waxay ka gooysaa carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ee angiotensin II waxayna ku dheelitirtaa vasodilator angiotensin (1-7) (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay kala saari kartaa dhowr kale oo peptide ah, oo ay ku jiraan [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay xakameysaa isdhaafsiga xuubka ee SLC6A19, oo ah gaadiidka amino acid ee dhexdhexaadka ah waxaana la xiriiriyaa cudurka 'Hartnup'.
ACE2 oo ah borotiinka transmembrane wuxuu u shaqeeyaa sida barta ugu weyn ee unugyada lagu galo qaar ka mid ah cudurrada loo yaqaan 'coronavirus', oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus-ka mas'uulka ka ah SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (virus-ka mas'uulka ka ah COVID-19).
Si gaar ah, SARS-CoV iyo SARS-CoV2 oo ku xidhan borotiinka S1 ee ku jira domain-ka enzymatic ee ACE2 waxay keenaan endocytosis iyo kala guurka labada fayras iyo enzyme ee ku yaal unugyada gudaha.
Nidaamkan gelitaanka wuxuu sidoo kale u baahan yahay in borotiinka S uu ku shaqeeyo TMPRSS2 oo ah borotiinka serine-ka ee martida ah, oo xakameyntiisa ay hadda baaritaan ku jirto sidii daaweyn suurtagal ah. Tani waxay ka caawisay qaar inay u maleynayaan in hoos u dhigista heerarka ACE2 ee unugyada ay ka caawin karto la dagaalanka infekshanka.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, dhowr bulsho xirfadeed iyo hay'ado sharciyeed ayaa soo bandhigay caddayn ku saabsan in la taliyay in la sii wado daaweynta ACE inhibitor iyo ARB.
